WEBVTT

01:51.880 --> 01:57.340
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.420 --> 02:01.920
[Episode 32]

02:33.480 --> 02:34.480
After treatment,

02:34.970 --> 02:37.570
His Excellency's basically
out of danger now.

02:37.950 --> 02:40.520
The sedative I just gave him
will help him rest,

02:40.520 --> 02:42.780
and the rash will gradually fade as well.

02:42.980 --> 02:44.190
But I'm afraid

02:44.210 --> 02:46.870
you'll have to put in some extra effort
tonight.

02:46.990 --> 02:49.270
Lord Jiang, you mean...

02:50.000 --> 02:52.660
This allergic reaction may cause
skin itching.

02:52.960 --> 02:54.960
You'll need to keep a close eye on him

02:55.079 --> 02:56.840
and make sure he doesn't scratch it,

02:56.840 --> 02:57.840
or it could lead to

02:58.130 --> 02:59.550
sores and infection.

02:59.960 --> 03:02.020
I have to stay up and keep watch again?

03:04.130 --> 03:05.130
Yes, preferably.

03:26.050 --> 03:27.510
-Lord Jiang.
-Lord Jiang.

03:28.890 --> 03:30.210
Come here. Come here.

03:31.840 --> 03:32.560
Lord Jiang.

03:34.050 --> 03:34.980
Did you tell her?

03:36.560 --> 03:37.400
I did.

03:37.770 --> 03:39.530
I've instructed Miss Wei

03:39.940 --> 03:42.000
to keep a close eye on His Excellency.

03:44.770 --> 03:45.560
Shisan.

03:46.340 --> 03:48.520
I've done all I can for you.

03:48.930 --> 03:49.950
The rest

03:50.329 --> 03:52.079
is up to you to figure out.

03:53.800 --> 03:55.050
Is this really a good idea?

03:55.050 --> 03:56.450
If Miss Wei

03:56.450 --> 03:58.010
finds out that His Excellency
is actually Gao Ran,

03:58.010 --> 03:59.560
the consequences would be disastrous.

03:59.560 --> 04:00.210
And

04:00.640 --> 04:02.770
if Zheng Tao caught
even the slightest hint of it,

04:02.770 --> 04:03.680
we'd be in trouble.

04:03.680 --> 04:05.360
It's not as serious as
you're making it out to be.

04:05.360 --> 04:06.490
Shisan

04:06.490 --> 04:08.600
can be a bit free-spirited,

04:08.890 --> 04:10.380
but she knows
how to see the bigger picture.

04:10.380 --> 04:11.730
As long as we explain things clearly
to her,

04:11.730 --> 04:14.130
she'll cooperate better than anyone else.

04:14.960 --> 04:16.730
You can't hide the look in your eyes

04:16.730 --> 04:17.990
when you like someone.

04:21.360 --> 04:22.240
Is that so?

04:23.360 --> 04:24.240
How do you know?

04:25.290 --> 04:25.910
I...

04:33.050 --> 04:34.440
When Fan Yun was here,

04:34.560 --> 04:36.260
you enjoyed eating pomelos.

04:36.650 --> 04:38.200
How come the pomelo I gave you

04:38.200 --> 04:40.130
ended up making you suffer so much?

04:43.980 --> 04:46.810
The thing is, when Gao Ran left,
I promised him

04:46.880 --> 04:48.280
I'd take good care of you.

04:48.730 --> 04:50.640
But now look at what I've done.

04:58.730 --> 05:00.680
Gao Ran should have arrived in Jing City

05:00.680 --> 05:02.330
by now, right?

05:05.850 --> 05:08.200
The same moon shines on us even though
we're thousands of miles apart.

05:08.200 --> 05:09.800
Make sure to take good care of yourself

05:09.800 --> 05:11.200
and don't catch a cold.

05:13.360 --> 05:14.360
Heaven help me—

05:14.360 --> 05:15.570
if there's a chance,

05:15.600 --> 05:17.780
could you let me see Gao Ran
one more time?

05:17.780 --> 05:18.980
Just once is all I ask.

05:44.000 --> 05:45.400
Don't touch my headband.

05:45.710 --> 05:46.600
Don't touch me.

05:49.200 --> 05:49.810
You...

05:49.830 --> 05:50.830
No scratching.

05:50.860 --> 05:52.320
Stop scratching. Stop it.

05:55.780 --> 05:58.610
I want water. I want water.

05:58.640 --> 06:00.520
Okay, I'll get it for you now.

06:00.560 --> 06:01.410
Don't worry,

06:01.410 --> 06:03.320
I'll take good care of you here all night.

06:03.320 --> 06:04.920
Tell me if you need anything.

06:05.490 --> 06:07.220
But you can't scratch anymore.

06:10.120 --> 06:11.520
Don't touch my headband.

06:20.700 --> 06:21.660
Impressive.

06:24.610 --> 06:26.000
How did he do that?

06:34.830 --> 06:36.150
Bravo!

06:41.440 --> 06:42.090
I want 4.

06:42.090 --> 06:43.240
Sure. Four for you guys.

06:43.240 --> 06:44.500
Here, hold this first.

06:49.930 --> 06:51.330
What's wrong, Tian Xing?

06:52.650 --> 06:53.650
Our money's gone.

06:54.440 --> 06:55.610
The money's gone?

06:57.560 --> 06:58.420
Where are they?

07:00.670 --> 07:01.260
Sir,

07:01.610 --> 07:03.390
where are those street performers
from earlier?

07:03.390 --> 07:04.440
They left a while ago.

07:04.440 --> 07:05.200
They left in such a hurry

07:05.200 --> 07:07.400
that they didn't even collect the tips.

07:10.560 --> 07:11.490
Those people...

07:12.290 --> 07:12.850
Oh no.

07:14.420 --> 07:15.310
The official seal is gone.

07:15.310 --> 07:16.240
-What?
-What?

07:19.540 --> 07:22.900
[Jing City]

07:23.930 --> 07:26.490
What are the Zheng family members
up to these days?

07:26.490 --> 07:28.970
They're probably busy
preparing for the clan leader election.

07:28.970 --> 07:31.320
Jin looks like
he's determined to win this time,

07:31.320 --> 07:34.720
so I suppose he's already planning
the celebration banquet.

07:35.530 --> 07:39.190
The new clan leader will be selected
from the younger generation.

07:39.560 --> 07:41.560
Don't you want to be the clan leader?

07:41.560 --> 07:42.240
Me?

07:43.680 --> 07:45.440
I don't think it's my turn yet.

07:46.360 --> 07:48.760
Jin has always been favored
by Grandfather,

07:48.760 --> 07:49.850
and in recent years,

07:49.850 --> 07:51.909
he's been the one managing Jing City.

07:52.680 --> 07:53.360
I...

07:56.970 --> 07:57.650
But

07:58.000 --> 07:59.760
Shi, I think you could give it a shot.

07:59.760 --> 08:01.620
You might actually have a chance.

08:03.240 --> 08:04.570
So what do you want to do?

08:06.680 --> 08:08.360
It's a bit embarrassing to say,

08:08.360 --> 08:09.160
but actually,

08:09.180 --> 08:10.640
I'd like to learn more from

08:10.650 --> 08:12.180
Lady Fan Yun and the others.

08:12.800 --> 08:14.530
You want to become an official?

08:15.760 --> 08:17.620
But I'm not particularly gifted,

08:17.760 --> 08:20.200
so I never had the courage
to sit for the selection exams.

08:20.200 --> 08:22.090
This time, I finally worked up
the courage to try,

08:22.090 --> 08:24.000
but then the selection exam
was reformed,

08:24.000 --> 08:26.650
and Grandfather just decided
not to let me participate.

08:26.650 --> 08:28.440
Good things never come easy.

08:28.440 --> 08:30.200
Once I become the clan leader,

08:30.200 --> 08:32.330
no one will be able to stand in your way.

08:35.010 --> 08:37.070
The official seal and money are gone,

08:37.600 --> 08:39.679
and there's no way to recover them
for now.

08:39.679 --> 08:40.770
But

08:40.770 --> 08:41.970
let's not lose heart.

08:42.840 --> 08:44.320
We'll figure something out.

08:44.320 --> 08:45.720
Don't you agree, Fan Yun?

08:51.010 --> 08:52.010
Actually,

08:52.600 --> 08:53.890
this is what

08:54.680 --> 08:56.680
the Governor often tells me as well.

08:56.680 --> 08:57.540
What about you?

08:58.010 --> 09:01.290
It must've been the Governor
who taught you this too, right?

09:01.290 --> 09:03.050
To keep a level head

09:03.050 --> 09:04.290
and stay optimistic.

09:05.010 --> 09:06.470
Isn't that right, Gao Ran?

09:10.770 --> 09:12.900
Yes, I learned that from the Governor.

09:13.200 --> 09:14.200
After all,

09:14.200 --> 09:17.200
keeping a gloomy face
won't solve anything.

09:17.200 --> 09:19.800
Your mindset shapes
the world you experience.

09:22.010 --> 09:23.250
So that's how it is.

09:30.530 --> 09:32.170
Then I have a question for you.

09:32.170 --> 09:33.170
Why is it

09:33.630 --> 09:35.330
that you learned nothing of

09:35.650 --> 09:38.050
Gao Ran's temperament and true character,

09:38.130 --> 09:39.250
Your Excellency?

09:43.450 --> 09:45.360
Cut it out. How much longer
are you planning to keep up this act,

09:45.360 --> 09:46.270
Governor?

10:07.530 --> 10:08.250
Zheng Xi.

10:08.740 --> 10:10.150
Look who's here.

10:09.560 --> 10:12.100
[Zheng Xi, Daughter of the Zheng family]

10:18.650 --> 10:19.440
Zheng Xi.

10:19.570 --> 10:21.330
Shi finally came home.

10:21.440 --> 10:22.410
Say something.

10:24.590 --> 10:26.160
Shi, I...

10:27.410 --> 10:28.320
It's okay.

10:28.650 --> 10:29.770
Don't force her.

10:30.680 --> 10:31.940
She's all grown up now,

10:32.130 --> 10:34.190
yet she's still just as quiet as ever.

10:35.610 --> 10:36.220
By the way,

10:36.680 --> 10:37.290
this

10:37.840 --> 10:39.930
is a hairpin I brought
especially for you from Ling'an.

10:39.930 --> 10:40.590
Have a look.

10:43.440 --> 10:44.250
Do you like it?

10:49.440 --> 10:52.300
You still dote on Zheng Xi
just like you always have.

10:52.560 --> 10:54.320
With an older brother like you,

10:54.320 --> 10:57.010
I'm afraid she'll have a hard time
finding a husband in the future.

10:57.010 --> 10:59.600
Zheng Xi is actually great at
managing the household.

10:59.600 --> 11:00.650
Over the years,

11:00.650 --> 11:02.960
she's been the one
handling all the household affairs.

11:02.960 --> 11:03.680
So,

11:03.680 --> 11:04.720
Shi, if you need anything,

11:04.720 --> 11:06.050
just go straight to her.

11:07.720 --> 11:10.050
I do need your help right now.

11:10.480 --> 11:11.930
Tidy up a few rooms for me.

11:12.000 --> 11:13.600
We'll be having guests over.

11:19.680 --> 11:21.410
You'd already thought of that?

11:22.130 --> 11:23.130
I told you.

11:23.800 --> 11:26.400
She's a real expert
at managing the household.

11:42.600 --> 11:43.530
Alright,

11:44.410 --> 11:45.540
tell me everything.

11:47.050 --> 11:49.050
How did you find out who I really was?

11:51.320 --> 11:53.200
It was pretty obvious.

11:53.200 --> 11:55.200
Everyone should have figured it out.

11:55.200 --> 11:55.720
I...

11:56.480 --> 11:57.320
Besides,

11:57.720 --> 11:59.370
the way you conduct yourself
and handle things

11:59.370 --> 12:01.440
is completely opposite to Gao Ran's.

12:01.440 --> 12:03.570
I should have noticed it much earlier.

12:05.660 --> 12:07.590
I really couldn't hide it from you.

12:10.290 --> 12:11.600
In that case,

12:12.290 --> 12:13.950
the one in the Qi Residence...

12:14.130 --> 12:15.390
Of course it's Gao Ran.

12:15.800 --> 12:16.730
But don't worry.

12:17.040 --> 12:18.320
Gao Ran is your brother

12:18.410 --> 12:20.130
and the person I trust the most.

12:20.130 --> 12:21.600
We trained together for a long time,

12:21.600 --> 12:22.650
and we are of one mind.

12:22.650 --> 12:24.180
There won't be any problem.

12:27.320 --> 12:28.010
Alright.

12:28.480 --> 12:29.800
Although I don't know

12:29.800 --> 12:31.440
exactly how you managed to

12:31.440 --> 12:33.320
switch identities with Gao Ran,

12:35.170 --> 12:38.010
since you are traveling
under Gao Ran's identity,

12:38.960 --> 12:40.760
from now on,

12:41.010 --> 12:42.940
you'll have to do everything I say.

12:43.080 --> 12:44.050
Of course.

12:44.440 --> 12:46.010
In Jing City, you're the gate commander,

12:46.010 --> 12:47.070
and I'm your guard.

12:47.370 --> 12:48.650
I'll naturally do as you say.

12:48.650 --> 12:49.290
Alright?

12:52.650 --> 12:55.940
[Jing City]

12:56.900 --> 12:58.230
Come here for a check.

12:58.950 --> 12:59.950
Pass. Pass.

13:00.410 --> 13:01.010
Next.

13:02.200 --> 13:02.960
Sir.

13:03.320 --> 13:04.290
Why are the guards at the city gate

13:04.290 --> 13:06.440
not wearing official uniforms?

13:06.440 --> 13:07.840
They're the Zheng family's guards,

13:07.840 --> 13:09.080
not official guards.

13:09.450 --> 13:10.780
The Zheng family's guards

13:10.780 --> 13:12.600
even have jurisdiction over this?

13:12.600 --> 13:14.480
They can get involved if they want to.

13:14.480 --> 13:15.600
During the clan leader election,

13:15.600 --> 13:17.250
outsiders aren't allowed to enter the city
on their own,

13:17.250 --> 13:17.840
unless

13:17.840 --> 13:19.680
they have documents
proving their identity.

13:19.680 --> 13:22.340
See? I need an official document
just to go home.

13:22.370 --> 13:23.570
Can you believe that?

13:27.930 --> 13:29.460
What's your business here?

13:30.050 --> 13:30.800
Let go of me!

13:33.010 --> 13:34.560
Seeing is believing.

13:35.290 --> 13:36.080
The Jing City

13:36.840 --> 13:39.300
has truly become
the Zheng family's domain.

13:39.560 --> 13:40.320
Turn around.

13:40.930 --> 13:42.560
We won't enter the city for now.

13:42.560 --> 13:43.320
Turn around.

14:06.870 --> 14:07.670
Grandfather.

14:09.320 --> 14:10.610
We're finally home.

14:11.130 --> 14:12.990
Granduncle worked so diligently

14:13.410 --> 14:15.560
to serve the Nine Cities
for so many years.

14:15.560 --> 14:16.760
Who would've thought

14:17.050 --> 14:18.560
he'd end up like this?

14:19.250 --> 14:20.930
The Zheng family is still here.

14:20.930 --> 14:21.990
And I'm still here.

14:23.530 --> 14:25.190
I won't let Grandfather down.

14:30.250 --> 14:33.580
Why didn't you tell me
you were coming back to Jing City, Shi?

14:34.130 --> 14:35.250
Don't you have any regard for me,

14:35.250 --> 14:38.320
the future clan leader
of the Zheng family?

14:41.080 --> 14:42.410
The future clan leader?

14:46.720 --> 14:48.450
Jin, you really are determined

14:48.510 --> 14:49.750
to get that position.

14:52.480 --> 14:53.770
In all of Jing City,

14:54.440 --> 14:55.970
who dares to compete with me

14:56.840 --> 14:58.070
for what I want?

15:02.840 --> 15:04.580
If there's nothing else, Jin,

15:05.250 --> 15:06.650
I'll head back to my room.

15:11.770 --> 15:14.680
You only managed to secure a place
in the Zheng family

15:14.680 --> 15:17.320
because you had Granduncle backing you.

15:17.700 --> 15:19.760
Now that Granduncle has passed away,

15:20.170 --> 15:21.170
your support has crumbled.

15:21.170 --> 15:23.080
I advise you to see things clearly

15:23.440 --> 15:25.170
and start showing some respect

15:26.770 --> 15:29.030
for the rules you're supposed to follow.

15:31.110 --> 15:32.310
This place

15:32.400 --> 15:34.130
truly hasn't improved one bit—

15:35.370 --> 15:37.630
neither the place itself nor the people.

15:51.770 --> 15:52.410
Ma'am.

15:53.750 --> 15:55.110
Can I help you?

15:55.850 --> 15:57.760
My lady and I are passing by

15:57.840 --> 15:59.130
and would like to stay here for the night.

15:59.130 --> 16:00.460
Would that be possible?

16:01.250 --> 16:02.250
Sure, sure.

16:02.250 --> 16:02.800
Thank you.

16:02.800 --> 16:03.650
Come in.

16:03.650 --> 16:04.560
Come on in!

16:04.580 --> 16:05.110
Come on.

16:05.170 --> 16:05.810
Let's go.

17:19.089 --> 17:21.500
♪ Wind sheds rain like tears ♪

17:21.520 --> 17:23.069
♪ Over the whole town ♪

17:23.099 --> 17:25.750
♪ At the second our gazes meet ♪

17:25.780 --> 17:29.340
♪ Past memories roar one louder beat ♪

17:36.650 --> 17:37.520
Gao Ran?

17:38.760 --> 17:39.570
I'm not him.

17:42.020 --> 17:43.650
Oh heavens.

17:44.020 --> 17:45.890
Could it be that I've been
thinking about him day and night

17:45.890 --> 17:47.420
that I actually saw Gao Ran?

17:47.890 --> 17:49.000
No way.

17:49.050 --> 17:50.860
W-Was that a dream?

17:50.880 --> 17:51.520
Gao Ran?

17:51.680 --> 17:52.930
You must have been dreaming.

17:52.930 --> 17:53.890
No, I wasn't.

17:53.890 --> 17:55.240
I saw your face.

17:55.240 --> 17:56.480
Then turn around and let me see.

17:56.480 --> 17:57.610
How inappropriate!

18:02.820 --> 18:03.950
Y-Your Excellency.

18:04.340 --> 18:05.410
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

18:05.410 --> 18:06.710
Maybe I...

18:06.900 --> 18:08.140
I-I was too desperate just now

18:08.140 --> 18:09.070
and saw it wrong.

18:11.620 --> 18:12.590
You may leave.

18:14.520 --> 18:16.440
No. I still have to take care of you.

18:16.440 --> 18:17.300
Not necessary.

18:20.240 --> 18:21.790
T-Then I'll leave.

19:42.280 --> 19:44.330
Why are you still up?

19:46.440 --> 19:47.570
Aren't you the same?

19:51.810 --> 19:54.240
After sleeping out in the open
all these days,

19:54.240 --> 19:55.300
now that I suddenly

19:55.610 --> 19:56.860
have a bed to sleep on,

19:57.330 --> 19:58.990
I actually can't fall asleep.

20:01.220 --> 20:05.480
It's more like you're worried about
not being able to enter Jing City, right?

20:09.680 --> 20:10.590
Don't worry.

20:11.850 --> 20:13.610
I believe Heaven will bless us.

20:14.440 --> 20:14.910
Here.

20:18.890 --> 20:19.550
Qi Zheng.

20:20.720 --> 20:21.760
Actually,

20:22.480 --> 20:23.730
I'm quite glad

20:24.680 --> 20:25.770
that you

20:27.620 --> 20:28.820
came along this time.

20:30.610 --> 20:31.520
It's nothing.

20:32.170 --> 20:34.650
I'm now your and Tian Xing's
personal military officer,

20:34.650 --> 20:36.580
so of course I'll be following you.

20:40.090 --> 20:42.520
Actually, ever since I became an official,

20:43.410 --> 20:45.240
I've always been prepared to go

20:46.440 --> 20:47.770
wherever I was assigned

20:48.040 --> 20:50.370
on my own.

20:50.850 --> 20:52.370
I never thought

20:53.570 --> 20:54.850
there would be someone

20:55.090 --> 20:56.690
who'd always stay by my side.

20:58.520 --> 20:59.650
Not even Gao Ran,

20:59.650 --> 21:00.520
because

21:01.760 --> 21:02.570
he has

21:03.170 --> 21:04.760
his own life too.

21:07.960 --> 21:09.620
So, are you trying to thank me?

21:12.320 --> 21:13.920
Making me a cup of tea will do.

21:16.940 --> 21:18.990
[Sweet Dew Tea]

21:29.570 --> 21:30.370
I...

21:33.440 --> 21:35.100
Forget it if you don't want to.

21:52.130 --> 21:52.860
I do.

21:57.170 --> 21:58.170
What did you say?

22:00.520 --> 22:01.350
I...

22:03.220 --> 22:04.610
I said I do.

22:28.720 --> 22:31.860
♪ Watch how many flowers
bloom and wither ♪

22:32.280 --> 22:35.710
♪ Count how many springs
and autumns pass ♪

22:36.080 --> 22:38.640
♪ Why the sighs and regrets? ♪

22:44.700 --> 22:48.190
♪ Lovers wait a lifetime ♪

22:48.750 --> 22:51.940
♪ Feelings that can't be severed ♪

22:52.690 --> 22:55.440
♪ How to let go? ♪

22:54.020 --> 22:54.610
What,

22:56.960 --> 22:58.620
do you not want to drink it now?

23:00.940 --> 23:04.290
♪ All our fates were long inscribed ♪

23:04.630 --> 23:08.290
♪ How to set free grief and joy? ♪

23:08.860 --> 23:10.580
♪ Mortal life is but an ephemeral dream ♪

23:09.270 --> 23:10.270
Come closer.

23:10.990 --> 23:16.540
♪ No mortal soul may rule its life ♪

23:14.440 --> 23:15.650
Closer.

23:16.920 --> 23:18.410
♪ If women are akin to blossoms ♪

23:18.450 --> 23:20.790
♪ Can they be cherished tenderly? ♪

23:20.950 --> 23:24.120
♪ For whom do they hide tears silently? ♪

23:24.400 --> 23:26.620
♪ How could one bear to lay blame? ♪

23:25.610 --> 23:26.960
What?

23:26.640 --> 23:29.010
♪ Time runs wild with reckless haste ♪

23:26.960 --> 23:28.170
Do you

23:28.170 --> 23:29.680
want me to feed you or something?

23:29.040 --> 23:32.740
♪ Never mind that
fate dyes pureness crimson red ♪

23:33.050 --> 23:34.390
♪ For whom does ♪

23:34.410 --> 23:36.580
♪ This phoenix flower bloom? ♪

23:36.610 --> 23:40.580
♪ Love fills my years,
and my heart remains true ♪

23:40.810 --> 23:42.860
♪ Let all worldly longing fade away ♪

23:42.890 --> 23:45.280
♪ Fall deep within a single dream ♪

23:45.300 --> 23:54.040
♪ Wait till a breath of wind arrives ♪

24:11.240 --> 24:14.590
♪ All our fates were long inscribed ♪

24:14.680 --> 24:18.340
♪ How to set free grief and joy? ♪

24:18.840 --> 24:20.560
♪ Mortal life is but an ephemeral dream ♪

24:20.970 --> 24:26.520
♪ No mortal soul may rule its life ♪

24:26.970 --> 24:28.460
♪ If women are akin to blossoms ♪

24:28.500 --> 24:30.840
♪ Can they be cherished tenderly? ♪

24:30.200 --> 24:31.200
Is this tea

24:31.000 --> 24:34.170
♪ For whom do they hide tears silently? ♪

24:31.890 --> 24:32.810
good?

24:34.450 --> 24:36.670
♪ How could one bear to lay blame? ♪

24:36.690 --> 24:39.060
♪ Time runs wild with reckless haste ♪

24:39.090 --> 24:42.790
♪ Never mind that
fate dyes pureness crimson red ♪

24:42.880 --> 24:44.220
♪ For whom does ♪

24:44.390 --> 24:46.560
♪ This phoenix flower bloom? ♪

24:46.590 --> 24:50.560
♪ Love fills my years,
and my heart remains true ♪

24:50.640 --> 24:52.690
♪ Let all worldly longing fade away ♪

24:52.720 --> 24:55.110
♪ Fall deep within a single dream ♪

24:55.350 --> 25:05.720
♪ Wait till a breath of wind arrives ♪

25:35.240 --> 25:37.130
Make sure to eat your fill.

25:37.130 --> 25:39.060
-Thank you.
-I'll get more for you.

25:50.480 --> 25:51.280
Good morning.

25:52.620 --> 25:53.210
Morning.

25:56.960 --> 25:58.480
Ma'am, let us help you.

25:58.710 --> 25:59.340
No need.

26:00.090 --> 26:01.330
Make sure you eat your fill.

26:01.330 --> 26:02.520
-Ma'am.
-Thank you, Ma'am.

26:02.520 --> 26:04.130
There's a strong scent of books
in this house.

26:04.130 --> 26:05.480
Is there a scholar living here?

26:05.480 --> 26:06.610
My eldest son

26:06.610 --> 26:07.700
loves to read.

26:07.890 --> 26:08.760
You see, he finally got the chance

26:08.760 --> 26:11.890
he'd been waiting for
after the selection exams were reformed,

26:11.890 --> 26:13.950
so he went to Ling'an to take the exam.

26:14.480 --> 26:16.160
Although he didn't rank among the top,

26:16.160 --> 26:17.430
he did fairly well

26:17.810 --> 26:18.850
and

26:18.850 --> 26:21.820
was appointed to
some minor official position

26:22.200 --> 26:23.330
or something.

26:23.330 --> 26:24.540
It really is

26:24.670 --> 26:27.360
a great blessing for our family.

26:28.040 --> 26:30.520
It seems the governor of the Nine Cities
is truly wise and capable.

26:30.520 --> 26:31.960
This selection exam reform policy

26:31.960 --> 26:33.280
has truly benefited
people across the land.

26:33.280 --> 26:34.090
Indeed.

26:34.760 --> 26:35.610
Then Ma'am,

26:35.610 --> 26:37.720
now that your son has become an official,

26:37.720 --> 26:38.650
why didn't you

26:38.650 --> 26:39.960
go to Ling'an with him?

26:40.680 --> 26:42.130
It's because of my youngest son.

26:42.130 --> 26:44.040
He never gives me a moment's peace.

26:44.040 --> 26:46.610
He's a bit scatterbrained.

26:46.610 --> 26:47.890
Whenever he sees

26:48.440 --> 26:51.090
something fun, he wants to learn it.

26:51.680 --> 26:52.720
Now

26:52.720 --> 26:54.960
he's taken a liking to magic tricks

26:54.960 --> 26:57.440
and spends all day hanging around

26:57.650 --> 26:59.450
with that troupe of performers.

26:59.590 --> 27:00.140
Look,

27:00.170 --> 27:01.830
he still hasn't come home yet.

27:02.040 --> 27:03.000
Magic tricks?

27:03.680 --> 27:04.520
Ma'am,

27:04.890 --> 27:07.000
may I ask where the magic trick troupe is?

27:07.000 --> 27:08.000
It's quite close.

27:08.130 --> 27:09.170
Not far from here.

27:09.520 --> 27:11.040
The people in that troupe

27:11.040 --> 27:12.370
are no good.

27:12.850 --> 27:15.080
They often use their magic tricks

27:15.170 --> 27:18.040
as a cover for petty theft.

27:18.040 --> 27:20.930
I told my son not to go there anymore,

27:20.930 --> 27:23.370
but he wouldn't listen.

27:23.370 --> 27:24.170
So, Ma'am,

27:24.170 --> 27:25.500
what's your son's name?

27:25.960 --> 27:27.040
Zhou Dangfan.

27:27.760 --> 27:28.810
Zhou Dangfan?

27:29.760 --> 27:31.130
That's enough about hhim.

27:31.130 --> 27:32.660
I'll go get you more dishes.

27:34.370 --> 27:36.780
It seems we searched high and low,

27:36.810 --> 27:38.720
only to find it right in front of us.

27:38.720 --> 27:39.930
Those who stole from us

27:39.930 --> 27:41.190
should be right there.

27:41.850 --> 27:43.310
I'll go retrieve them now.

27:45.130 --> 27:46.170
I'll go with you.

27:46.960 --> 27:48.200
You all stay here.

27:48.200 --> 27:49.650
More people will only
make things complicated.

27:49.650 --> 27:50.910
I'll be back in no time.

27:52.810 --> 27:53.720
Be careful.

27:56.000 --> 27:56.730
Don't worry.

28:10.450 --> 28:13.430
[Liu Mu, Gate Commander of Jing City]

28:19.280 --> 28:19.960
Waiter.

28:20.180 --> 28:21.520
Bring me another steamer of buns.

28:21.520 --> 28:22.570
Coming right up.

28:25.090 --> 28:26.570
Here are your buns.

28:27.150 --> 28:28.480
Take your time, Sir.

28:30.720 --> 28:31.240
Sir,

28:31.680 --> 28:33.280
you certainly have quite an appetite.

28:33.280 --> 28:34.410
You've polished off 6 steamers of buns

28:34.410 --> 28:36.040
in a blink of an eye.

28:36.610 --> 28:37.480
Waiter, check please.

28:37.480 --> 28:38.330
Coming.

28:38.900 --> 28:41.230
It's so delicious. Why aren't you eating?

28:41.520 --> 28:42.850
How could I bring myself to eat this?

28:42.850 --> 28:45.260
I've had enough of these cheap joints.

28:45.370 --> 28:47.330
Let's not come to places
like this anymore.

28:47.330 --> 28:48.410
We'll go to a fancy restaurant

28:48.410 --> 28:49.520
next time and see

28:49.520 --> 28:51.330
what the food there tastes like.

28:51.330 --> 28:54.390
A fancy restaurant?
Do you even have the money for that?

28:54.460 --> 28:55.610
You have no idea.

28:55.630 --> 28:58.190
Our Boss got his hands on
a treasure today.

28:58.280 --> 28:59.610
From now on, Jing City

28:59.610 --> 29:01.170
will belong to our Boss.

29:01.170 --> 29:01.960
When that happens,

29:01.960 --> 29:03.330
we'll be able to eat at

29:03.330 --> 29:05.730
whichever restaurant we want
in Jing City.

29:07.200 --> 29:07.960
Really?

29:08.520 --> 29:09.380
What treasure?

29:09.960 --> 29:10.520
The...

29:13.330 --> 29:14.930
The gate commander's official seal.

29:14.930 --> 29:16.610
By then, we'll present this official seal
to the Zheng family.

29:16.610 --> 29:17.930
Surely they'll reward us with

29:17.930 --> 29:19.370
plenty of gold and silver.

29:19.370 --> 29:20.850
Who would still bother
eating these lousy buns then?

29:20.850 --> 29:21.370
Waiter!

29:21.960 --> 29:22.890
Bring the check.

29:22.890 --> 29:23.760
Coming.

29:24.850 --> 29:26.850
Did you enjoy your meal, gentlemen?

29:27.760 --> 29:28.690
Keep the change.

29:29.040 --> 29:30.300
Thank you, gentlemen.

29:30.780 --> 29:31.820
Please take care.

29:32.280 --> 29:33.540
Take care. Come again.

29:36.130 --> 29:37.330
Where did this guy go?

29:37.570 --> 29:39.330
He hasn't paid for the buns!

29:39.330 --> 29:40.260
He ate that much.

29:40.570 --> 29:41.370
Where is he?

29:42.810 --> 29:44.000
Where did he go?

29:44.720 --> 29:46.140
He ate 7 steamers of buns!

29:50.210 --> 29:51.330
Congratulations, Boss.

29:51.330 --> 29:52.410
Today's haul

29:52.410 --> 29:53.850
was incredibly rewarding.

29:53.850 --> 29:55.170
Here, Boss, a toast to you.

29:55.170 --> 29:56.330
Come on, Boss.

29:56.520 --> 29:57.840
I told you,

29:58.130 --> 30:00.390
as long as you stick with me
and work hard,

30:00.480 --> 30:02.760
I'll make sure you live high on the hog.

30:02.760 --> 30:04.650
-Come on, cheers.
-Come on, cheers.

30:04.650 --> 30:06.090
Come, bottoms up.

30:11.480 --> 30:12.240
Zhou Dangfan!

30:12.240 --> 30:13.170
Serve the dishes already!

30:13.170 --> 30:14.580
Where's my roast chicken?

30:14.580 --> 30:16.510
Coming right up. Just a moment.

30:26.960 --> 30:27.760
Zhou Dangfan.

30:28.890 --> 30:31.440
Stop rushing me.
I told you to stop rushing me.

30:31.440 --> 30:32.640
I'm the only one here,

30:32.720 --> 30:34.280
and I can barely keep up.

30:34.280 --> 30:36.540
I don't even have anyone
to lend me a hand.

30:36.720 --> 30:38.720
Why are you working all by yourself?

30:39.610 --> 30:41.130
How come I've never seen you?

30:41.130 --> 30:41.890
Who are you?

30:42.380 --> 30:44.040
You don't need to know who I am.

30:44.070 --> 30:45.530
But I came from your house.

30:45.890 --> 30:47.810
Your mother's urging you to go home.

30:47.810 --> 30:49.740
But I'm here to learn magic tricks.

30:50.500 --> 30:51.370
I haven't learned any.

30:51.370 --> 30:52.930
I've just been cooking all day.

30:52.930 --> 30:54.730
Once I master them, I'll go back.

30:55.760 --> 30:56.680
You know what?

30:57.070 --> 30:58.370
What they teach you here

30:58.370 --> 30:59.870
are just ordinary magic tricks,

30:59.870 --> 31:01.800
like conjuring birds and flowers.

31:02.420 --> 31:03.930
But it's different with me.

31:03.930 --> 31:06.090
I know magic that's far more advanced
and mysterious.

31:06.090 --> 31:07.090
Do you want to learn?

31:07.090 --> 31:08.170
You know magic tricks?

31:08.170 --> 31:08.890
Of course.

31:09.520 --> 31:10.650
Then show me one.

31:18.520 --> 31:19.280
Did I do it?

31:20.330 --> 31:20.930
You did.

31:21.330 --> 31:23.370
So you... You really know magic tricks.

31:23.370 --> 31:24.170
Want to learn?

31:24.860 --> 31:25.590
Yes.

31:25.620 --> 31:27.570
Go home right now if you want to learn.
I'll be there in a minute.

31:27.570 --> 31:29.630
Then... Then I'll go home right away.

31:36.150 --> 31:37.100
That Zhou Dangfan.

31:37.100 --> 31:38.430
He's so slow at cooking.

31:39.610 --> 31:40.410
You...

31:40.410 --> 31:41.370
Who are you?

31:45.260 --> 31:46.320
Smells wonderful.

31:47.040 --> 31:48.410
A table full of delicious food and wine.

31:48.410 --> 31:49.070
What,

31:49.220 --> 31:51.750
you're enjoying a feast
without inviting me?

31:52.180 --> 31:53.420
Invite you?

31:54.610 --> 31:55.930
Do I know you?

31:56.810 --> 31:58.280
You do look familiar.

31:59.610 --> 32:01.850
Have we met somewhere before?

32:02.130 --> 32:03.390
Met somewhere before?

32:04.330 --> 32:05.480
Let me think.

32:07.030 --> 32:07.890
I remember now.

32:07.930 --> 32:08.810
At the market,

32:08.810 --> 32:09.930
you even made a bouquet of flowers appear

32:09.930 --> 32:11.390
from my companion's arms.

32:13.890 --> 32:14.240
He...

32:14.240 --> 32:15.280
It's you.

32:15.280 --> 32:15.960
It's him.

32:15.960 --> 32:16.850
Buddies!

32:16.850 --> 32:17.780
Get him!

32:22.430 --> 32:23.450
When we see Boss later,

32:23.450 --> 32:24.880
let's flatter him with
some auspicious words.

32:24.880 --> 32:25.930
That way, when he hands out the rewards,

32:25.930 --> 32:27.130
we can get a little extra.

32:27.130 --> 32:28.280
Of course.

32:28.280 --> 32:29.090
From now on,

32:29.090 --> 32:31.200
we'll eat whatever we want.

32:31.520 --> 32:33.780
We won't be eating steamed buns anymore.

32:39.650 --> 32:40.680
Hey, who are you?

32:40.680 --> 32:41.410
What do you want?

32:41.410 --> 32:43.670
Good mutts don't get in the way. Get lost.

32:44.370 --> 32:46.630
Did you not hear me?
I told you to get lost.

32:52.820 --> 32:54.350
Where's the official seal?

32:54.600 --> 32:55.730
What official seal?

32:55.840 --> 32:57.200
We don't know.

32:57.290 --> 32:58.810
We really don't know.

33:04.130 --> 33:05.660
Where's the official seal?

33:05.700 --> 33:07.210
Our Boss has it.

33:07.440 --> 33:08.760
Where's your Boss?

33:09.680 --> 33:11.040
Whoever has the pouch

33:11.040 --> 33:12.280
is our Boss.

33:19.330 --> 33:20.240
Help!

33:20.520 --> 33:21.680
Someone, save me!

33:22.130 --> 33:24.330
You can't just leave me to die!

33:27.610 --> 33:28.440
Tell me.

33:29.200 --> 33:31.060
Where did the contents of this go?

33:32.000 --> 33:32.760
Who are you?

33:32.760 --> 33:33.980
Why should I tell you?

33:34.370 --> 33:34.830
Come on.

33:35.200 --> 33:36.680
Be gentler,

33:36.680 --> 33:37.520
and faster.

33:39.890 --> 33:41.650
Whose underling are you?

33:41.650 --> 33:43.580
Do you guys still work for me or not?

33:45.240 --> 33:46.000
Then,

33:46.370 --> 33:48.090
take off his other shoe too.

33:48.090 --> 33:49.620
Tickle both feet together.

33:50.640 --> 33:51.890
I won't say a word even if you kill me.

33:51.890 --> 33:53.640
Kill me... Kill me if you can!

33:57.130 --> 33:57.960
Take it off.

33:59.330 --> 34:02.690
I'll talk! I'll tell you everything!

34:02.890 --> 34:03.540
Speak.

34:04.610 --> 34:06.760
I knew stealing an official seal
was a serious crime,

34:06.760 --> 34:08.690
so once I obtained it,

34:08.690 --> 34:09.520
I handed it

34:09.770 --> 34:10.850
over to someone.

34:11.440 --> 34:12.250
To whom?

34:12.929 --> 34:14.000
To

34:14.000 --> 34:14.730
the Zheng family.

34:14.730 --> 34:16.060
Who in the Zheng family?

34:16.520 --> 34:17.560
Who else could it be?

34:17.560 --> 34:18.560
Zheng Jin,

34:18.850 --> 34:19.730
of course.

34:21.620 --> 34:22.739
Zheng Jin?

34:25.810 --> 34:26.850
What are you still doing here?

34:26.850 --> 34:27.670
Get lost!

34:28.969 --> 34:30.159
Stop untying the rope!

34:30.159 --> 34:32.020
Carry me away. Just carry me away!

34:32.850 --> 34:33.370
Boss.

34:33.370 --> 34:34.560
This is our place.

34:34.560 --> 34:35.080
Where can we possibly go?

34:35.080 --> 34:36.690
Cut the crap and just go.

34:40.520 --> 34:41.960
Zheng Jin...

34:48.080 --> 34:50.960
I obtained the newly appointed
gate commander's official seal.

34:50.960 --> 34:52.020
The official seal?

34:55.250 --> 34:55.810
Jin,

34:56.250 --> 34:57.650
why did you take her seal?

34:58.330 --> 34:59.730
What else could it be for?

35:00.000 --> 35:01.440
Besides,

35:01.440 --> 35:04.440
isn't everything I do
for the sake of our Zheng family?

35:06.690 --> 35:09.960
No wonder there's been no news
from them these past few days.

35:09.960 --> 35:11.690
It seems they failed to enter the city

35:11.690 --> 35:13.220
without the official seal.

35:14.000 --> 35:16.810
You and Grandfather went to Ling'an
to ask for the gate commander position

35:16.810 --> 35:18.370
but failed.

35:18.410 --> 35:20.670
I was thinking about what to do with them,

35:20.720 --> 35:22.930
and now they've walked
right into my hands.

35:22.930 --> 35:24.460
It's as if fate is on my side.

35:26.210 --> 35:27.410
There's no time left.

35:27.600 --> 35:28.120
This...

35:28.480 --> 35:29.040
Jin.

35:29.660 --> 35:31.910
They are officials from the Nine Cities.

35:31.910 --> 35:33.640
They'll enter the city sooner or later.

35:33.640 --> 35:35.840
Isn't it a bit too risky for us
to do this?

35:36.210 --> 35:37.080
You...

35:37.080 --> 35:39.160
Why don't you give it a second thought?

35:39.160 --> 35:40.480
Let's return this official seal

35:40.480 --> 35:41.600
back to them.

35:42.370 --> 35:43.290
Useless.

35:43.690 --> 35:44.890
You wish.

35:45.520 --> 35:48.330
It's true they're officials
appointed by the Nine Cities,

35:48.330 --> 35:49.640
but isn't there a saying?

35:49.640 --> 35:52.410
"The mountains are high
and the emperor is far away."

35:52.410 --> 35:53.520
Jin, are you planning to...

35:53.520 --> 35:55.050
Without the official seal,

35:55.480 --> 35:57.730
who would know they are gate commanders?

35:57.730 --> 35:59.160
Send a letter to Ling'an,

35:59.770 --> 36:01.640
saying that on their way here,

36:01.640 --> 36:03.970
they were ambushed and killed by bandits.

36:04.520 --> 36:06.770
At worst, we'll only be blamed morally.

36:08.560 --> 36:10.960
No one will be able to
find any fault with us.

36:41.770 --> 36:42.690
Gao Ran?

36:43.660 --> 36:44.300
Freeze!

36:44.330 --> 36:45.330
Stop running!

36:45.930 --> 36:46.890
Stop right there!

36:46.890 --> 36:48.090
Hurry up and get them!

36:48.290 --> 36:49.290
Get them!

36:51.480 --> 36:52.410
Don't let them escape!

36:52.410 --> 36:53.410
Freeze!

36:53.640 --> 36:55.300
-Stop right there!
-Get them!

36:55.560 --> 36:56.960
Get them! Get them!

36:59.030 --> 37:00.230
-Over there!
-Hurry!

37:02.560 --> 37:04.250
-Stop!
-Just leave me behind.
-No way.

37:04.250 --> 37:05.600
You're a friend that I, Liu Mu, value.

37:05.600 --> 37:07.460
How could I just leave you behind?

37:15.080 --> 37:15.640
Gao Ran.

37:15.920 --> 37:17.180
I can only escort you this far.

37:17.180 --> 37:18.250
For the rest of the journey,

37:18.250 --> 37:19.440
you're on your own.

37:20.210 --> 37:21.140
Hurry and leave!

37:26.440 --> 37:27.080
Liu Mu!

37:28.770 --> 37:29.500
Don't worry.

37:30.000 --> 37:30.770
I won't die.

37:32.140 --> 37:33.400
Take care of yourself.

37:33.890 --> 37:35.000
You mustn't die.

37:38.730 --> 37:39.370
Someday,

37:39.890 --> 37:41.290
we'll meet again!

37:42.000 --> 37:43.770
Liu Mu!

38:04.770 --> 38:05.370
Gao Ran?

38:06.850 --> 38:08.250
It really is you, Gao Ran.

38:08.600 --> 38:09.250
Me?

38:10.490 --> 38:12.150
Yeah... Yeah, it really is me.

38:12.560 --> 38:13.820
You don't remember me?

38:15.560 --> 38:17.480
Years ago at the Shadow Slay League,

38:17.480 --> 38:17.960
you

38:18.290 --> 38:18.750
and I...

38:19.120 --> 38:19.850
The two of us.

38:22.650 --> 38:23.680
Side by side.

38:25.410 --> 38:26.130
Fought.

38:27.850 --> 38:29.410
You pulled me along as we ran away.

38:29.410 --> 38:30.210
That's right.

38:31.440 --> 38:32.840
I knew you'd remember me.

38:34.290 --> 38:36.950
I definitely wouldn't forget.
Definitely not.

38:41.080 --> 38:42.440
Even in the depths of the night,

38:42.440 --> 38:44.410
that horrific battle

38:44.410 --> 38:46.290
still lingers in my dreams.

38:46.770 --> 38:48.120
So it's you.

38:48.120 --> 38:48.850
Yes.

38:49.440 --> 38:49.930
It's me.

38:51.640 --> 38:52.600
So I am...

38:53.040 --> 38:54.160
You are...

38:55.520 --> 38:58.160
You haven't changed a bit, bro.

38:59.410 --> 39:00.740
So what are you here for?

39:01.160 --> 39:02.250
I came to look for something.

39:02.250 --> 39:02.780
Alright,

39:02.960 --> 39:03.890
keep looking then.

39:03.890 --> 39:04.750
I'll leave now.

39:23.960 --> 39:25.620
What kind of illusion is this?

39:26.990 --> 39:28.950
He looks exactly like Gao Ran.

39:32.640 --> 39:33.570
He's not Gao Ran.

39:34.990 --> 39:36.920
How could Gao Ran not recognize me?

39:45.290 --> 39:47.590
I wasted all that time
searching for the official seal.

39:47.590 --> 39:51.250
His Excellency is still waiting for me
to return and report to him.

40:08.410 --> 40:09.330
You're back.

40:09.330 --> 40:10.080
How did it go?

40:10.080 --> 40:11.810
Did you find the official seal?

40:13.040 --> 40:14.480
The official seal had been taken away.

40:14.480 --> 40:16.740
It's now in the hands of the Zheng family.

40:19.120 --> 40:19.690
Buddy.

40:20.080 --> 40:21.280
You're finally back.

40:21.440 --> 40:23.240
Hurry and teach me magic tricks.

40:26.210 --> 40:27.160
Who is this?

40:27.850 --> 40:28.770
Zhou Dangfan.

40:31.770 --> 40:33.130
W-What magic tricks?

40:33.210 --> 40:34.470
You know magic tricks?

40:37.330 --> 40:38.530
Nothing impressive.

40:39.210 --> 40:39.810
Wait,

40:39.830 --> 40:41.060
you don't know?

40:41.120 --> 40:41.600
His face...

40:41.600 --> 40:43.600
It changed just like that!

40:44.520 --> 40:45.780
Have you never seen it?

40:49.020 --> 40:51.020
-We know. We know.
-Now you know.

40:51.050 --> 40:52.620
Then hurry up and teach me.

40:54.080 --> 40:55.120
Rest early.

40:56.010 --> 40:56.660
Alright.

40:56.690 --> 40:58.290
Then we'll head back and rest.

40:58.290 --> 41:00.160
Take your time with the tricks.

41:00.160 --> 41:01.210
Rest early.

41:01.210 --> 41:02.040
-Hurry up and teach me.
-We're going to bed.

41:02.040 --> 41:03.120
How on earth did you do that?

41:03.120 --> 41:04.080
I'll go get some props.

41:04.080 --> 41:04.810
Okay.

41:05.120 --> 41:06.040
Wait for me.

41:06.040 --> 41:07.210
I'll wait for you.

41:07.210 --> 41:08.040
Wait for me.

41:08.770 --> 41:09.920
I'll be waiting.

41:19.690 --> 41:20.440
Ma'am.

41:20.640 --> 41:22.820
You mean Miss Fan Yun went to make money?

41:22.820 --> 41:23.860
Yes.

41:23.930 --> 41:24.810
Early this morning,

41:24.810 --> 41:27.630
she came to borrow some writing supplies
from me.

41:28.290 --> 41:29.170
She said

41:29.480 --> 41:32.280
she was going to figure out a way
to make some money.

41:36.480 --> 41:37.230
Ma'am.

41:37.690 --> 41:39.150
Do you know where she went?

41:39.440 --> 41:41.200
I think she went

41:41.640 --> 41:43.370
to the market.

41:52.330 --> 41:58.260
[Letter-writing Service]

42:02.960 --> 42:05.520
Freshly steamed buns!

42:05.520 --> 42:07.250
Thin skin, big filling!

42:07.770 --> 42:08.900
Come in and try some!

42:14.380 --> 42:16.700
I noticed you've been waiting here
for almost 2 hours,

42:16.700 --> 42:18.120
and you haven't had a single customer.

42:18.120 --> 42:18.890
Why not

42:18.890 --> 42:21.220
buy some buns from me
to fill your stomach?

42:22.480 --> 42:23.440
But...

42:24.080 --> 42:25.730
I have no money, Boss.

42:26.520 --> 42:27.820
You're quite honest.

42:28.030 --> 42:29.210
Yesterday, a customer

42:29.210 --> 42:29.930
ate so many buns here,

42:29.930 --> 42:31.370
but he didn't even pay.

42:31.520 --> 42:33.450
Just thinking about it makes me...

42:33.920 --> 42:35.130
Speak of the devil.

42:36.290 --> 42:37.090
Get over here!

42:37.370 --> 42:38.970
You ate my buns yesterday,

42:39.080 --> 42:40.310
but you didn't even pay.

42:40.310 --> 42:41.500
I'm here to pay you.

42:42.050 --> 42:43.370
Give me 2 more steamers of buns

42:43.370 --> 42:44.230
and pack them up for me.

42:44.230 --> 42:45.430
I have to hit the road.

42:48.240 --> 42:50.160
As long as you've got the money,
that's no problem.

42:50.160 --> 42:51.360
Write a letter for me.

42:52.640 --> 42:53.490
Great.

42:53.930 --> 42:55.130
Finally, a customer.

42:55.360 --> 42:55.950
Sir.

42:56.330 --> 42:57.410
What would you want me to write?

42:57.410 --> 42:58.250
Write exactly

42:58.250 --> 42:58.960
as I say.

43:00.250 --> 43:00.960
Go ahead.

43:01.370 --> 43:02.500
I managed to escape.

43:03.690 --> 43:05.690
I still have some things to take care of.

43:05.690 --> 43:07.490
I'll come find you once I'm done.

43:08.080 --> 43:10.540
I have something very important
to tell you.

43:12.210 --> 43:13.080
And?

43:13.730 --> 43:14.330
That's it.

43:14.560 --> 43:15.150
But

43:15.330 --> 43:17.000
there has to be some kind of name
or address, right?

43:17.000 --> 43:17.890
What's your name,

43:17.890 --> 43:19.350
and who is this letter for?

43:19.690 --> 43:20.640
I almost forgot.

43:21.770 --> 43:23.100
I'll write this myself.

43:26.000 --> 43:26.560
Here.

43:36.800 --> 43:38.200
I can't really write,

43:38.330 --> 43:39.790
but I can draw pretty well.

43:46.810 --> 43:48.560
-A willow tree...
-Miss.

43:48.770 --> 43:51.690
Please send this letter
to Qi Residence in Ling'an for me.

43:51.690 --> 43:52.330
Okay.

43:59.440 --> 44:00.640
The Governor?

44:01.260 --> 44:02.890
Please come again.

44:07.410 --> 44:10.530
Buns for sale! Buns for sale!

44:10.640 --> 44:11.970
Thin skin, big filling!

44:12.930 --> 44:14.330
Care for some buns?

44:15.730 --> 44:17.190
Excuse me. Let me through.

44:17.290 --> 44:17.960
Excuse me.

44:20.190 --> 44:21.480
Let me through. Thanks.

44:21.480 --> 44:22.640
Thanks. Thanks.
